    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122240/extras/9dc4616b0d1b081dc64c1945ebc16af4.avif?t=1726827426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122240/extras_big/9dc4616b0d1b081dc64c1945ebc16af4.avif?t=1726827426 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Killer Night</strong></i> is an engaging psychological thriller in <i>visual novel</i> format that immerses players in a mysterious survival game. Set in a dark and isolated mansion, the participants must uncover the identity of a hidden killer among them. Every choice carries significant consequences, leading to different narrative paths and multiple endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a plot full of tension and twists, <i><strong>Killer Night</strong></i> explores the complexities of moral decisions and interpersonal relationships. The game introduces a unique meta-narrative, where the line between reality and fiction gradually blurs, keeping players constantly on edge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will not only have to survive but also reflect on their choices, with revelations that leave a lasting impact until the very last moment. <i><strong>Killer Night</strong></i> promises an interactive experience that maintains suspense, making each playthrough unique and unpredictable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122240/extras/8d9b6f0100b74d3b7f63097c20fdca38.avif?t=1726827426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122240/extras_big/8d9b6f0100b74d3b7f63097c20fdca38.avif?t=1726827426 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Thriller</strong>: An atmosphere full of tension and mystery that will keep you on edge from start to finish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Compelling Storyline</strong>: Uncover an intricate plot with unexpected twists and shocking revelations until the very end.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Characters</strong>: Each participant has a personal story and a reason for being there. Learn their secrets and decide who to trust.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration and Clues</strong>: Discover hidden passages and gather crucial clues to uncover the identity of the killer.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Critical Decisions</strong>: Your choices will shape the course of the game and determine who lives and who dies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122240/extras/b1e08757520b8a00d36fe66be415d327.avif?t=1726827426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122240/extras_big/b1e08757520b8a00d36fe66be415d327.avif?t=1726827426 width=800 height=260 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul>",
